<promed@promedmail.org>
[Queensland is in the process of eradicating TB. However, this is a major
outbreak. This outbreak may delay eradication attempts. Although there is
potentially a plan for compensating the owners, this many animals
represents more than most eradication attempts have in the budget. It will
be interesting to see if they can actually eradicate TB within the goals
previously set. -Mod.TG]
